CustomField.description: Number of days between the time the Contract was sent to the customer and it was received by Qualcomm.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: If the Sent to Customer date is blank, the Signed by Cust (Days) is blank. If the Sent to Customer date is populated, the field is calculated by the Contract Received minus the Sent to Customer date.
CustomField.label: Signed by Cust (Days)
